Class Family

java.lang.Object
fitnessclub.Member
fitnessclub.Family
All Implemented Interfaces:

public class Family extends Member
This class represents a family membership type in the fitness club. This is a subclass of Member and includes specific functionality, such as billing and guest pass.
Author:
Ved Patel, Vivek Manthri
